=== Enlargement ===
Associate Members, Candidates:
* {{Flagu|Serbia}} became a candidate for accession to CERN on 19 December 2011, signed an association agreement on 10 January 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.b92.net/info/vesti/index.php?yyyy=2012&mm=01&dd=10&nav_category=1331&nav_id=572568 |title=Vesti – Srbija zvanično postala član CERN-a |publisher=B92 |date= |accessdate=4 July 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://cms.web.cern.ch/news/serbia-expected-become-cern-associate-member |title=Serbia expected to become CERN Associate Member |website=CMS Experiment web site |publisher=CERN |date=18 January 2012 |accessdate=5 July 2014}}</ref> and became an associate member in the pre-stage to membership on 15 March 2012.<ref name=SRB />
* {{Flagu|Turkey}} signed an association agreement on 12 May 2014<ref name=TUR>{{cite web |url=https://home.cern/about/updates/2014/05/turkey-become-associate-member-state-cern |website=CERN press release |publisher=CERN |title=Turkey to become Associate Member State of CERN |date=12 May 2014 |accessdate=5 July 2014}}</ref> and became an associate member on 6 May 2015.
*{{Flagu|Pakistan}} signed an association agreement on 19 December 2014<ref name=PAK>{{cite web |url=http://www.mofa.gov.pk/pr-details.php?prID=2050 |title=Pakistan Becomes the First Associate CERN Member from Asia |website=Government of Pakistan press releases |publisher=Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Government of Pakistan |date=20 June 2014 |accessdate=5 July 2014}}</ref> and became an associate member on 31 July 2015.<ref>{{cite web|title = Pakistan becomes Associate Member State of CERN |url = https://home.cern/about/updates/2015/07/pakistan-becomes-associate-member-state-cern|website = CERN|accessdate = 2015-08-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = Pakistan officially becomes an associate member of CERN - The Express Tribune|url = http://tribune.com.pk/story/930265/pakistan-officially-becomes-an-associate-member-of-cern/|accessdate = 2015-08-01}}</ref>
* {{Flagu|Cyprus}} signed an association agreement on 5 October 2012 and became an associate Member in the pre-stage to membership on 1 April 2016.<ref name="cyprus-assoc" />
* {{Flagu|Ukraine}} signed an association agreement on 3 October 2013. The agreement was ratified on 5 October 2016.<ref name="ukraine"/>
* {{Flagu|India}} signed an association agreement on 21 November 2016.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://press.cern/press-releases/2016/11/india-become-associate-member-state-cern |title=India to become Associate Member State of CERN |date=21 November 2016}}</ref> The agreement was ratified on 16 January 2017.<ref name="india" />
* {{Flagu|Slovenia}} was approved for admission as an Associate Member state in the pre-stage to membership on 16 December 2016.<ref name="slovenia-assoc"/> The agreement was ratified on 4 July 2017.<ref name="slovenia-assoc-ratify"/>
* {{Flagu|Lithuania}} was approved for admission as an Associate Member state on 16 June 2017. The association agreement was signed on 27 June 2017 and ratified on 8 January 2018.<ref name="lithuania-assoc-lrp">{{cite web|url=https://www.lrp.lt/en/press-centre/press-releases/lithuania-has-become-associate-member-of-cern/27822|title=Lithuania has become associate member of CERN|author=|date=|website=www.lrp.lt}}</ref><ref name="lithuania-assoc-cern">{{cite web|url=https://home.cern/about/updates/2018/01/lithuania-becomes-associate-member-state-cern|title=Lithuania becomes Associate Member State of CERN|author=Harriet Kim Jarlett|date=8 January 2018|website=CERN}}</ref>

